rows.label: tlk41100171_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, hey! Are you good
at catching bugs?

rows.label: tlk41100171_04_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm making an insect specimen
collection right now!

rows.label: tlk41100171_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm almost done, but I just can't
seem to find the last one I need—

rows.label: tlk41100171_04_msg0004
rows.name:
I've looked all over for it...
Maybe it doesn't live around here?

rows.label: tlk41100171_04_msg0005
rows.name:
If only I had someone who knew
a lot about insects with me, I
could find it in a flash—
